    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;WebRTC is a protocol suite for use with real-time applications that can be deployed in browsers -- "real-time communication on the Web".  This document defines the WebRTC threat model and analyzes the security threats of WebRTC in that model.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
